  "container-shutdown-warning.txt":
    '🚨 CONTAINER SHUTDOWN WARNING\n=============================\n\nOrganization: {{organizationName}}\n\nURGENT: Your container will be shut down in 48 hours!\n\nYour account has insufficient credits to continue running your deployed container. Add funds within the next 48 hours to prevent service interruption.\n\n⏰ TIME UNTIL SHUTDOWN: 48 Hours\n   Scheduled: {{shutdownTime}}\n\n📦 CONTAINER DETAILS\n--------------------\nContainer Name: {{containerName}}\nProject: {{projectName}}\nDaily Cost: ${{dailyCost}}/day\nCurrent Balance: ${{currentBalance}}\nRequired to Continue: ${{requiredCredits}}\n\n⚡ WHAT HAPPENS WHEN SHUTDOWN OCCURS?\n-------------------------------------\n• Container will be stopped - Your agent will go offline\n• API endpoints will become unavailable\n• Data in memory will be lost (persistent storage retained for 30 days)\n\n💳 ADD CREDITS NOW\n------------------\nVisit: {{billingUrl}}\n\n💡 QUICK COST REFERENCE\n-----------------------\nContainers are billed daily at ${{dailyCost}}/day (${{monthlyCost}}/month).\nAdd at least ${{minimumRecommended}} to keep your container running for the next week.\n\n---\nQuestions? Reply to this email or visit your dashboard: {{dashboardUrl}}\n\n© {{currentYear}} Eliza Cloud. All rights reserved.\n\nYou received this urgent alert because your container "{{containerName}}" is scheduled for shutdown due to insufficient credits.\n',
